Youri::Factory
--------------

Factory methods

Description
-----------
YOURI stands for "Youri Offers an Upload & Repository Infrastucture". It aims
to build tools making management of a coherent set of packages easier.

This class provides factory methods for dynamically creating instances.

Installation
------------
To install, just use:
perl Makefile.PL
make
make test

